  "detailed_description": "Welcome to the Gunship video game.<br>GUNSHIP is a short single-player 3D simulation game.<br>Experience that will take you into the cockpit of the most fearsome aircraft ever built.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368650/extras/d2bc87afab434971ee11446e321dc300.poster.avif?t=1751778184\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368650/extras/d2bc87afab434971ee11446e321dc300.webm?t=1751778184\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368650/extras/d2bc87afab434971ee11446e321dc300.mp4?t=1751778184\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Gunship is all about precision and accuracy, and players will need to master the controls of the aircraft to successfully complete their missions. With realistic physics and advanced AI, the game offers a truly immersive experience that will keep you on the edge of your seat.<br><br>Whether you're a fan of action games or just looking for an exciting new challenge, Gunship is sure to deliver.",
  "about_the_game": "Welcome to the Gunship video game.<br>GUNSHIP is a short single-player 3D simulation game.<br>Experience that will take you into the cockpit of the most fearsome aircraft ever built.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368650/extras/d2bc87afab434971ee11446e321dc300.poster.avif?t=1751778184\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368650/extras/d2bc87afab434971ee11446e321dc300.webm?t=1751778184\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368650/extras/d2bc87afab434971ee11446e321dc300.mp4?t=1751778184\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Gunship is all about precision and accuracy, and players will need to master the controls of the aircraft to successfully complete their missions. With realistic physics and advanced AI, the game offers a truly immersive experience that will keep you on the edge of your seat.<br><br>Whether you're a fan of action games or just looking for an exciting new challenge, Gunship is sure to deliver.",
